<script setup lang="ts">import { computed } from 'vue'; import { ImageOff } from '@lucide/vue'; const props=defineProps<{ title:string; image?:string; meta?:string; badges?:string[] }>(); const failed=defineModel<boolean>('failed',{default:false}); const src=computed(()=>props.image || '/static/img/no_poster.svg');</script>
<template><article class="panel group overflow-hidden"><div class="relative aspect-[2/3] overflow-hidden bg-[var(--surface-muted)]"><img v-if="!failed" :src="src" :alt="`${title} 海报`" loading="lazy" class="h-full w-full object-cover transition duration-500 group-hover:scale-[1.035]" @error="failed=true"/><div v-else class="muted grid h-full place-items-center"><ImageOff :size="30"/></div><div v-if="badges?.length" class="absolute left-2 top-2 flex flex-wrap gap-1"><span v-for="badge in badges" :key="badge" class="badge bg-white/90 text-slate-700 shadow-sm">{{ badge }}</span></div></div><div class="p-3"><h3 class="line-clamp-2 min-h-10 text-sm font-extrabold leading-5">{{ title }}</h3><p v-if="meta" class="muted mt-1 truncate text-xs">{{ meta }}</p><slot /></div></article></template>
